primarily due to increased material costs; and (5) decreased wholesale volumes.
We view the Chinese market as important to our global growth strategy and are employing a multi-brand strategy. In the coming
years we plan to leverage our global architectures to increase the number of product offerings under the Buick, Chevrolet and
Cadillac brands in China and continue to grow our business under the local Baojun and Wuling brands. We operate in the Chinese
market through a number of joint ventures and maintaining strong relationships with our joint venture partners is an important part
of our China growth strategy.
