agreements with SoftBank Vision Fund (AIV M2), L.P. (SoftBank), which triggered SoftBank's obligation to purchase additional
Cruise convertible preferred shares for $1.35 billion. We expect SoftBank to complete the purchase of the majority of such
additional preferred shares in the first quarter of 2022 and any balance by the end of 2022. Cruise will need one additional permit
from the CPUC, which it has applied for, to commercially deploy such vehicles with paying passengers in California.
