that our supply needs for production are met or are not disrupted. Our variable interests in these nonconsolidated VIEs include
equity investments, accounts and loans receivable, committed financial support and other off-balance sheet arrangements. The
carrying amounts of assets were $846 million and liabilities were insignificant related to our
